channel.title: What to do with "cannot find process java"
channel.description: This is getting very frustrating and everything is working perfectly HOPEFULLY except my voule restarter. It is saying cannot find process java during restarts. How can I fix this. I am using jdk6u2 and did the classpath and the paths. My compiler is working fine, my runserver is working fine, what am I doing wrong......?
